PQEmVzO6NSBkmajOQuNz_-y1j9aE-IMxAT35GA", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "heather-chang-a449b2242", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAADxN2lQBXuJ1dVViNGlrqhNZdizlP68le-Q", "profilePic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEiVB862EoBbw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1683953504585?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=oAXRFrMU_FumIssFbNBWRS8jFfPSkuAwOUwPRpuorQc", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEiVB862EoBbw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1683953504585?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=oAXRFrMU_FumIssFbNBWRS8jFfPSkuAwOUwPRpuorQc", "publicIdentifier": "charlie-springthorpe-1b3b625b", "recommendations/0/context": "Charlie was Emily's client", "recommendations/0/date": "April 29, 2021", "recommendations/0/description": "I worked with Emily on multiple PR campaigns from mass brands such as the Robinsons-Wimbledon partnership, to smaller up-and-coming brands such as Aqua Libra. Emily was brilliant at delivering fresh ideas for all budgets and I thoroughly enjoyed working with her. Her enthusiasm and passion for the campaigns was brilliant and very well balanced with her drive for tracking and proving the results. ", "recommendations/0/name": "Emily Morgan", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "MD Operations & Innovation, ESG Lead & Senior Communications Consultant", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/emily-morgan-2a6839/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAfkV4Bq7vE0WIKz1lfBor5GSwoY9Mg_i0", "recommendations/1/context": "Yvonne was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendations/1/date": "July 16, 2020", "recommendations/1/description": "Yvonne was the Flavour Concentrate Global Marketing Manager whilst I worked in the UK Robinsons Team. I was fortunate enough to work really closely with Yvonne on one of my projects. She is a brilliant strategic thinker and had a real skill for presenting plans and bringing senior stakeholders along the journey with her. Yvonne was proactive in her approach and always bought out of the box ideas to the table. Being as passionate for insight driven strategies as she was, Yvonne really helped me to widen my thinking and become a better marketeer. I would love to work with Yvonne again as I believe she is an amazing asset to any team and a brilliant mentor. ", "recommendations/1/name": "Yvonne Broomham", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Product Marketing Manager", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yvonne-broomham/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFKZI0BmOe80b3gZhZyRxg8Kv4Ttp4jzt0", "recommendations/2/context": "Neil was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendations/2/date": "July 16, 2020", "recommendations/2/description": "I worked with Neil at Think Management and reported to him for a couple of key clients. He always had an amazing positive attitude and positive work ethic. He has a great strategic and analytical brain and always looked beyond the possible to develop out of the box solutions. Neil was a pleasure to work with and I would strongly recommend him as he was an amazing asset to have on the team. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Neil Laverty ", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Growth Guru - Rewarded UA, Performance Marketing, CRM, Angel Investor, Startups, Fractional GTM, Data & Analytics", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/neil-laverty/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABJ4ucMBFvil6APaSAiQtJtEmFBOTUfOifs", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "David worked with Charlie but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "September 12, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Charlie is a great team player, brings lots of energy and enthusiasm and a desire to make a difference. Her passion shines through and helps inspire customers/colleagues understand how the brand she is working will add value to their business or customers.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "David Greenaway", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Plenish Head of Sales Hospitality Team", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-greenaway-877002132/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACBkclsBnt369vDNF68RxT95x_iY8huE0_g", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Amy worked with Charlie on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "July 29, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Charlie has a infectious energy and passion for the brands she works on. Working with Charlie on Aqua Libra it was clear to see that she was a real team player and put her all into anything she worked on. Great at inspiring cross functional teams & instilling belief when faced with a challenge! Strong vision for the brand but with an eye for detail. Really enjoyed my time working with Charlie and wish her every success!", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Amy Boustred", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Marketing & Innovation Controller", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/amyboustred/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAx1MpYB3KT1aLiCt6lfttbSA80rT_1Y0t0", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Sophie was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "July 25, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Charlie is a great asset to any team! Enthusiastic, full of passion and a hard worker. She’s an excellent project manager, has a keen eye for detail and her energy is contagious. I thoroughly enjoyed my time working with her within the Robinsons team!", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Sophie Killer-Lloyd", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Creative, commercial FMCG marketer with 8+ yrs’ experience driving growth through brand strategy 🎯, innovation 🚀 & insight 💡. Curious thinker, confident doer and passionate about turning insight into action.", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sophie-killer-lloyd-15752989/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABLD65MBJgWP9Qevsk7AWmOJZ0i8vtlfHAA", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Bruce was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "July 21, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Charlie is an energetic self starter with a positive can do attitude. I enjoyed working with Charlie and have no doubt that she will be an asset to whatever business she joins.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Bruce Dallas", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Vice President, Commercial Strategy & Planning", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/brucedallas/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAXd-FgBIBjCHCYZV63__MV9v9HELPj8hl8", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Charlie was Zaine's client", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "July 21, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Charlie and I have worked across several big campaigns over the last two years, with highlights including the Robinsons-Wimbledon Activation and Aqua Libra 'Liberate your Lunchbreak' campaign.\n\nCharlie has a keen eye for detail and isn't afraid to push creative boundaries and norms. Throughout my time working with Charlie, I have been impressed with how she briefs and communicates with myself and my team. She brings a brilliant amount of energy and enthusiasm to projects and is driven to achieve more with a creative approach. I'm always able to have open conversations with Charlie as she challenges me where appropriate, but is ultimately driven to finding the best solution for the brand.\n\nCharlie was a pleasure to work with and I hope to work with her again in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Zaine Venter", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Sports Partnerships & Sponsorship Activation Leader | Experiential & Live Events | Fan Engagement Platforms | Former Managing Director", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/zaine-venter-3a780210/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJBL68BOES6CIHsqk6MeN6R-6lRxGVSDs0", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Ilan managed Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "July 18, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Charlie was one of the best ABMs I have ever worked with. A phenomenal passion and work ethic, hugely proactive, who you could always trust to get things done. Charlie has great potential and I am confident has a very successful career in front of her.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Ilan Arkin", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Head of Brand & Shopper KP Snacks", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ilan-arkin-56791034/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAdBAB8Bs8R1yoIVNdLtRTn7GBASyewf0zg", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Adrian worked with Charlie on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "July 17, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "Charlie is an exceptionally hard worker, excelling in her tenacity and “nothing is impossible” attitude. A very personable character who is a great team player yet with that individual fire in her belly to persevere and overcome obstacles herself. A great asset to any team.", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Adrian Howe", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "at CarlsbergBritvic", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/adrian-howe-96723751/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAArkD58BD-FileaUlwA13uXeOwrzyWZqd8I", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Yvonne was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "July 16, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "I worked with Charlie on the flavour concentrate category and the Squash'd brand. She is a very creative marketeer, her approach is very analytical and insight-driven and she understands how to present to key stakeholder and customers. Charlie was responsible for a full pack re-design including the activation strategy and execution. She is confident in working in partnership with creative and packaging agencies and always delivers towards set timelines. I would love to work with Charlie again as she always stays on top of her projects and approaches challenges with a very positive mindset. I can highly recommend her, she will be an asset to any team or new challenge she approaches in her career.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Yvonne Broomham", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Product Marketing Manager", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yvonne-broomham/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFKZI0BmOe80b3gZhZyRxg8Kv4Ttp4jzt0", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Charlie was Mike's client", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "July 15, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "We worked for Charlie a couple of projects and observed her mix of hugely valuable skills. She is very task focussed but couples this with excellent relationship management abilities allowing her to get the best out of people whilst optimising the output. It was a pleasure to work for her and I know she will add huge value to any team and organisation. Would highly recommend and will hopefully work together in the future.   ", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Mike Dickson", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Owner Director at Melli", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mike-dickson-a3499b27/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWpxQgBy5Oio2BVgHM-njoxkUBoCE50yCg", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Davnet was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "July 15, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "It was a pleasure to work with Charlie on the Aqua Libra brand. A whip-smart marketer.  \nPassionate, strategic, always with her eye on the prize and hard to name another person I've worked with who has powered through more work in a shorter time period. The epitome of GSD!  \nWould love to work with her again on growing brands.\n", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Davnet Doran", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Global Head of PR / NED", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/davnet-doran/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPh7t4BximXt0Z3DVBMKVsbarNqZjtluVs", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Neil was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "July 15, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "I worked with Charlie on a couple of key clients at Think Management Consultancy. She has an inspirational work ethic and attitude that brought out of the box ideas to the table. Charlie is both data driven, autonomous and creative and I’d jump at the opportunity to work with her again the future.\n", "recommendationsReceived/10/name": "Neil Laverty ", "recommendationsReceived/10/subtitle": "Growth Guru - Rewarded UA, Performance Marketing, CRM, Angel Investor, Startups, Fractional GTM, Data & Analytics", "recommendationsReceived/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/neil-laverty/", "recommendationsReceived/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABJ4ucMBFvil6APaSAiQtJtEmFBOTUfOifs", "recommendationsReceived/11/context": "Yakov was senior to Charlie but didn't manage Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/11/date": "July 14, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/11/description": "During my time working with Charlie I have to admit that there was much I learnt from her.\nShe is wise beyond her years and always showed complete dedication to the job at hand , never missing a deadline and often going beyond her remit.\nI have no hesitation in recommending her to any potential employer as she would be an asset to their enterprise. ", "recommendationsReceived/11/name": "Yakov Moses", "recommendationsReceived/11/subtitle": "Genera Manager of National Commercial Sales Polaris Media and The Australian Jewish News", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yakov-moses-399ab25/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAENUqUB3TaXN6_NWUdi44-cy4F5Hzxcth8", "recommendationsReceived/12/context": "Phil managed Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "October 5, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "Charlie is without doubt one of the most talented employees I've had the fortune of working for me during my many years of being in business.\n\nOver the last two years she has assisted my consultancy business with a variety of tasks ranging from market research, presentations, copywriting, websites and general marketing work including a number of social media projects. I was confident every request would be delivered on time and to a high standard.\n\nMy only regret is that Charlie has now moved on.\n\nIf you have the opportunity to hire her, you are very lucky, so do it.", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Phil Shaw", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "Commercial Director | Chief Growth Officer | Board & Advisory | Regulated Digital, iGaming, Sports & Media | Founder & Exit Experience", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/phil-shaw/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAeTmgIB35Eea23xkVmnMUqhM38EiKnz-CE", "recommendationsReceived/13/context": "Jackie managed Charlie directly", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "September 28, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "During Charlie's two week internship, she tacked a wide variety of PR tasks with huge enthusiasm and commitment. She used her good writing skills and creativity to deliver engaging content and, with her extensive marketing knowledge, quickly gained an understanding