edia.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFvPVbW-DWhTw/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B56Z09IPihKgAM-/0/1774847067924?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=lUwG19zHPJ3xFjKQc-NgobFQKKkKmBoPbz23aQUmg7Q", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFvPVbW-DWhTw/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B56Z09IPihKgAM-/0/1774847067924?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=lUwG19zHPJ3xFjKQc-NgobFQKKkKmBoPbz23aQUmg7Q", "publicIdentifier": "matthieu-reynaud-2759b033", "recommendations/0/context": "Matthieu managed Roberto directly", "recommendations/0/date": "March 9, 2023", "recommendations/0/description": "Roberto is a true passionate Chef who is dedicated to his guests, his work and his team. Working with him was such a pleasure for me as him and I loved talking about food. Roberto is really creative & inventive in his cuisine. He created so many successful menus so he has guests following him all around the world!\nFor who ever will hire Roberto you can be sure to have a successful restaurant. And not to mention also Roberto is really a great human being with a big heart, honest and loyal. I'm glad I have worked with Roberto and he is still until today a great inspiration for me.", "recommendations/0/name": "Roberto P.", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Executive Italian Chef | International Culinary Consultant | Luxury Hotels & Resorts | Italian & Mediterranean Cuisine Specialist | Restaurant Openings & Concept Development", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/roberto-p-06496172/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA9yeQwBBsuFo8jpfppMM3Nl79D_7e3SUZE", "recommendations/1/context": "Matthieu managed Sam directly", "recommendations/1/date": "March 9, 2023", "recommendations/1/description": "Sam is a great person, smart, diligent, boundless with great leadership skills. He is a passionate F&B leader who knows how to lead/motivate/develop a team. During all these years I worked with Sam I always been impressed by his hardworking, his creativity and his constant self-motivation to improve himself and to learn. Sam is a gem and I'm confident he will be really successful. I hope we will work again together! Cheers", "recommendations/1/name": "Sam Ashworth", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "EAM | Director of Food & Beverage | Luxury | Asia", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sam-ashworth-b1242222/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAASwhb4Bk4STH5Dtz3UnnhZ3VksUvjarCZ8", "recommendations/2/context": "Matthieu managed Julien directly", "recommendations/2/date": "September 27, 2020", "recommendations/2/description": "Julien worked with me few years as Restaurant Manager when I was at Pathumwan Princess Hotel. I enjoyed working with Julien as he is really talented in F&B field. He is fantastic with guest, great as a leader and really knowledgeable in food & beverages. Always positive attitude and a smile on his face. \nI recalled Julien did create several successful F&B promotions, overseeing very well his restaurant (food cost, Bev cost, expenses and profit). I will have no hesitation to rehire Julien in any management role. Any organisation who will hire Julien will be lucky to have him and will have great return. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Julien Garrigou", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "In love with F&B and Hospitality", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/julien-garrigou-bb4779b1/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABfI3ngBavfRk8aum4TC7NxuC0xId2AnwYU", "recommendations/3/context": "Matthieu managed Florian directly", "recommendations/3/date": "May 6, 2016", "recommendations/3/description": "Florian Winkler is a very talented professional. Working with him was one of my best experience so far. He is energetic, smart, hard worker, unique service mind, great customer focus and what I liked the most with him his is great sens of humor. I would recommend Florian to any organization as having him into your team is a great asset for success!", "recommendations/3/name": "Florian Winkler", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Business Development Lead | Franchise Development, Lead Aquisition, Mergers & Acquisitions, International Development | QSR Expert | VP Level - C Suite Level Developing great brands across EMEA & APAC", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/florian-winkler-2b2a0b21/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAASZU-YBEj8z2L7akKBxhav2CxHwW8ZI7h0", "recommendations/4/context": "Matthieu managed Antoine directly", "recommendations/4/date": "October 8, 2015", "recommendations/4/description": "He was doing his internship with Room & Guest Service Division during the period April 27th to October 29th 2015.\nI’m truly proud to commend Antoine for his exemplary performance for front office operations and handling several projects with great success. \nI strongly recommend him for his future endeavor.\nAntoine is certainly an asset to any hotel that will accept him as an employee.\n", "recommendations/4/name": "Antoine Hesnard", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Francais", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/antoine-hesnard-9738968a/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABL_BucBKnSN6f-8SFNKqe58WETduqQBtvg", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Roberto worked with Matthieu on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "March 9, 2023", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I had the privilege and honor to work with Matthieu for almost 4 years, he was my General Manager at Phatumwan Princess Hotel in Bangkok,\nI learned a lot with him and I consider him a mentor, a person who, in addition to making you give your best, managed to bring out the talent that every collaborator did not know they had, makes you believe in yourself and every observation he made on the mistakes I made they were just to be able to improve A great leader capable of forming winning teams.\nFor me the best General Manager of my career,", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Roberto P.", 